      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把 Connector 画成一个子图，里面包含 worker 的核心步骤。第一步是不是要从 outbox 里 claim 一行数据，同时加上锁机制？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connector",
        "outbox row",
        "locked_by",
        "lock_expires_at"
