    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，claim 的时候要设置 locked_by 和 lock_expires_at，防止多个 worker 抢同一行。然后第二步是尝试调用 FHIR，用 conditional PUT 到 Patient 资源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "claim outbox row",
        "Attempt FHIR call",
        "conditional PUT",
        "Patient"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我在 Connector 子图里加上这两个步骤。接下来需要处理不同的响应结果对吧？成功、失败的情况都要覆盖。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "1",
        "2",
        "Connector"
